submission_title: UTSU reverts back to prior mental health coverage
author: wowrandomwow
body:
This is great news! Folks won't need to use that sketchy Google form funding model. Mental health coverage will stay the same as last year, $100 per session for $1500 max!

Good job to everyone who spoke up and
messaged them!

submission_title: UTSU reverts back to prior mental health coverage
author: crud_lover
body: Wow good news! Makes me wonder why the change was made in the first place...
